thread.title: Ralph
thread.title_full: Fromex True Black & White reviewed by Ralph

author: Ralph
title: Ralph
text: I couldn't find anyone I thought would do a good job printing my B&W pictures locally so went to Fromex and was pleased with the results. The high quality prints were mailed to me the next day but took a week to get to NC from CA, so if you don't live in CA and aren't in a great hurry, I would definitely recommend Fromex.
